DESCRIPTION:$0.00 - Tickets for the 8 PM screening of SIRAT 2025 • Moroc
 co\, France • 115 minutes • dir. Oliver Laxe Saturday\, March 28th at 
 Upland Wood Shop (354 W 11th St) FREE\, but ticketed | All Ages Showtime: 
 8pm *Sponsored by IU Arts &amp\; Humanities Council as part of Granfalloon
  2026. More info at grafalloon.indiana.edu . TRAILER Synopsis : A father (
 Sergi López) and his son arrive at a rave deep in the mountains of southe
 rn Morocco. They are searching for Mar — daughter and sister — who van
 ished months ago at one of these endless\, sleepless parties. Surrounded b
 y electronic music and a raw\, unfamiliar sense of freedom\, they hand out
  her photo again and again. Hope is fading\, but they push through and fol
 low a group of ravers heading to one last party in the desert. As they ven
 ture deeper into the burning wilderness\, the journey forces them to confr
 ont their own limits.
